01:26:32.520 --> 01:26:35.890
And those are not of the high attention

01:26:35.890 --> 01:26:37.580
kind of high emotionality

01:26:37.580 --> 01:26:41.170
or in the intensity of the experiences

01:26:41.170 --> 01:26:42.390
that I described today.

01:26:42.390 --> 01:26:45.980
Those are more about repetition
and reward and repeat,

01:26:45.980 --> 01:26:47.650
repetition, reward, repeat,

01:26:47.650 --> 01:26:51.420
